The paper discusses the intersection of RPA with AI and BPM, indicating a strong focus on artificial intelligence and robotics (cs.AI and cs.RO). The paper also discusses the challenges and potential solutions for injecting intelligence into RPA technology, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential impact of RPA on human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybersecurity (cs.CY).
